capstone.objects

Class Roster

  • java.lang.Object
    • capstone.objects.Roster

  • public class Roster
extends java.lang.Object
    Each roster correlates to a unique combination of a team and a season along with a list of skaters. A roster for the Chicago Blackhawks from the 2021-2022 season contains the players who were on their team that season. Rosters are from February 1st of the given year.
